61
00:03:40.927 --> 00:03:44.507
The rest of your body can only send about a billion.

62
00:03:45.319 --> 00:03:47.319
that means that sight will represent

63
00:03:47.319 --> 00:03:47.979
one third

64
00:03:49.159 --> 00:03:51.079
